00:00:16,220 --> 00:00:18,600
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:23,510
What a coincidence.

4
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:25,070
Where are you guys from?

5
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:27,390
Are you two on a date?

6
00:00:27,710 --> 00:00:30,480
Have you both cleared the air
and resolved all past misunderstandings?

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:32,960
I was just about to ask.

8
00:00:33,070 --> 00:00:34,840
How did you guys end up together?

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:37,490
Miss Gu and I are heading
to the tailor shop.

10
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:40,030
That's right.

11
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,070
Mr. Gao mentioned

12
00:00:41,070 --> 00:00:43,460
he's been in Rongcheng for days
and hasn't bought any new clothes.

13
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:45,280
He asked me for advice.

14
00:00:50,030 --> 00:00:51,600
We have something to handle first.

15
00:00:51,780 --> 00:00:53,320
I'll come back later and tell you more.

16
00:00:55,070 --> 00:00:56,030
Mr. Gao.

17
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,790
Shall we go now?

18
00:00:58,030 --> 00:01:00,200
If we're late,
the shop might close soon.

19
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:01,670
Let's go.

20
00:01:10,950 --> 00:01:12,560
The fries today were really good.

21
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,710
Let's meet again next time.

22
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,450
I know you're doing it out of spite,

23
00:01:16,710 --> 00:01:18,040
but I'm still very happy.

24
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,350
If you ever need anything in the future,

25
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,870
I'll always be there.

26
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,790
You decided to come back at last?

27
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:46,870
Of course.

28
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,060
It's time for dinner.

29
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:49,450
I need to be home for dinner.

30
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,710
Were you

31
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:54,280
with Gu Mengqiu all day today?

32
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,730
