52
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,360
Oh, by the way,

53
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,400
do you recall

54
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,750
Zhang Zhiran

55
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:44,800
