56
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,310
I always found this person

57
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,120
somewhat strange.

58
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,930
He was present at the scene
during the deaths

59
00:02:48,940 --> 00:02:50,110
of General Jin and Cao Liang.

60
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,190
