133
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,120
Miss Gu

134
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,390
is a regular customer here.

135
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,840
I naturally recall her preference for tea,

136
00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:08,650
so preparing it comes naturally to me.

137
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,550
Mr. Zhang,
you have always been so thoughtful.

138
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,270
As I should be.

139
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,360
Mr. Zhang.

140
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,720
Please display the suit fabrics

141
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,360
you have on hand

142
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,670
for Mr. Gao to have a look.

143
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:19,000
Certainly.

144
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:21,390
Hao, bring over the fabric.

145
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:22,440
Alright.

146
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,870
Mr. Zhang, having a customer

147
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,870
like Miss Gu

148
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,750
explains why your business
keeps growing.

149
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:29,460
Our profit margins are narrow,

150
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,480
so we greatly
value Miss Gu's continued patronage.

151
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:34,550
By the way,
Miss Gu also has many of the sachets

152
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,790
from your shop at her place.

153
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:36,960
