154
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,320
It's a tradition in Rongcheng.

155
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,750
Sachets symbolize safety and joy,

156
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:43,910
and people often buy them

157
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:45,080
to give to someone important.

158
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:47,320
Mr. Gao, would you like to pick one too?

159
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,510
How about this, Mr. Gao?

160
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,630
Hao.

161
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:52,000
Bring over the new batch

162
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,510
of sachets.

163
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:52,960
Alright.

164
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,510
Give to someone important?

165
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,240
Mr. Gao.

166
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,720
Please choose.

167
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:10,510
I'll get this one.

168
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:12,320
Our shop also offers embroidery services.

169
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,030
Mr. Gao.

170
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:15,200
