195
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:37,240
We aren't suited for each other.

196
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,960
We're not from the same world.

197
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,960
I know.

198
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,030
In the past,

199
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:41,960
